quran[34]{c,v,t,f}:
  74,52,"Yeti mundu jwalijose mwa ŵanganyao akusakaga ali apedwile ikalakala yeunukule-unukule (kuumila kwa Allah kutendela umboni yakuŵecheta Muhammadi ﷺ)."
  74,53,"Ngwamba! Nambo kuti ŵanganyao ngaakujijogopa Akhera."
  74,54,"Ngwamba! Chisimu jalakwe (Qur’aniji) jiŵele chikumbusyo."
  77,40,"Ipotesi lyele lisikulyo taachiipata ŵakanila."
  77,41,"Chisimu ŵakun'jogopa (Allah) chachiŵa m’miulili (jakusisimila chenene) ni achitutumule."
  77,42,"Ni isogosi yatachiilaluchilaga."
  78,37,"M'mbuje jwa kumawunde ni petaka ni yaili chilikati chakwe, Jwaukoto wejinji. Pangali ŵachachikola machili gakuŵecheta Najo."
  78,38,"Lisiku lyatiuchijima Nsimu (Jibulilu) pamo ni Achimalaika m’misela; ngasaŵecheta (jwalijose) ikaŵeje jwatachipedwa lusa ni (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji, ni tachiŵecheta yakulungamika."
  78,39,"Lyele ni Lisiku lyakuonaonape, basi jwaakusaka aliikolochesye chilepe malo gakuujila kwa M'mbujegwe (Allah)."
  79,31,"Ŵakopwesye mwalakwemo mesi gakwe ni mopo wakwe."
  79,32,"Nombe matumbi ŵagasimiiche."
  79,33,"(Kuŵa) yakunsengwasya ŵanganyammwe ni ilango yenu."
  80,28,"Kwisa soni isogosi ya zabibu ni maupulu (gakulya ilango)."
  80,29,"Ni kwisa soni isogosi ya zaituni (yakwenga mauta) ni itela yatende."
  80,30,"Ni migunda jaitela yejinji."
  81,25,"Soni aji (Qur’an) nganigaŵa maloŵe ga shetani jwakuŵinjidwa."
  81,26,"Nambi kwapi nkuja?"
  81,27,"Nganijiŵa aji (Qur’an) ikaŵeje chikumbusyo cha iwumbe yosope."
  82,19,"Lyele ni lisiku lyangakola mundu chilichose chanti ni kunkamuchisya mundu jwine. Nombe ulamusi (wosope) lyele lisikulyo uchiŵa wa Allah pe."
  83,16,"Kaneka chisimu ŵanganyao tachiujinjila Moto Waukali."
  83,17,"Kaneko ni kuchiŵechetedwa kuti: “Ayi ni ayilayila yamwaliji nkuikanila.”"
  83,18,"Yakuona! Chisimu yakulembedwa ya (masengo ga) atenda ngoto ili mu Illiyyun."
  84,13,"Chisimu jwalakwe jwaliji jwakusengwa (pajwaliji) ni achalongo achin'jakwe (ku duniya)."
  84,14,"Chisimu jwalakwe jwasimichisyaga kuti ngasaujila (kwa Allah)."
  84,15,"Elo! Chisimu Ambujegwe ŵaliji ali nkunnolechesya."
  85,10,"Chisimu aŵala ŵaŵalagasisye ŵakulupilila ŵachilume ni ŵakulupilila ŵachikongwe (pakwachoma moto) kaneka ni ngatenda toba, basi akwete kupata ilagasyo ya Jahannama, soni akwete kupata ilagasyo yakutinisya."
  85,11,"Chisimu aŵala ŵaakulupilile ni kutendaga yambone, akwete kupata Matimbe ga ku Mbepo gasikujilima cha pasi pakwe sulo. Kwalakweko nikupunda kwekulungwa."
  85,12,"Chisimu kapeleche ka ilagasyo ka Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) kaŵele kaukali nnope."
  86,4,"Pangali mundu jwalijose ikaŵeje kwa jwalakwejo kwana nkunnolela (jwaakusunga itendo yakwe)."
  86,5,"Basi achetelele mundu, ana agumbidwe kuumila ku chichi?"
  86,6,"Agumbidwe kuumila ku mesi gakusumbika."
  87,1,"Liswejesyani lina lya Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) Ŵapenani kusyene."
  87,2,"Aŵala ŵaŵagumbile (chilichose) ni kuchikolosya."
  87,3,"Soni Aŵala ŵaŵapimiile (chilichose mwachiichiŵeela) ni kuchijongolela (ku yaŵachipimileyo)."